  <brief_title>Effects of DASH Diet on Corticosteroids Medication Use</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 3 Study of Beneficiary Effects of Dietary Approaches to Stop Hypertension (DASH) on the Metabolic Aeffects of Corticosteroids Medications Use</official_title>
